author: Asa Fitch
title: Iranian Lawmakers Approve Nuclear Deal
text:
DUBAI—Iranian lawmakers on Tuesday approved the implementation of July’s historic nuclear deal with six world powers, removing one of the final obstacles within Iran’s system to the accord.
A majority of Iran’s parliament members approved the bill, which directs the government to put the deal in place, according to the official Islamic Republic...
